channel.title: [510] HD Client!
channel.description:
This is a completly working HD Client, And a loader that will load any client automatically, and can change the RSA key to a key you specify, Change to "0" to disable RSA. [b]Loader and HD Client[/b] - [url=http://rapidshare.com/files/151337007/SpuneRace_Loader2.rar.html]RapidShare[/url] Please also note that its GPL Source, If you build another loader off it, you must supply the source code and the GPL licence. Credits would be appreciated :) Enjoy. If you get an [B]error_game_dll[/B] try this:
I have been able to replicate the error. It looks like the official client and loader, save the dll's to "C:\WINDOWS\.jagex_cache_32\runescape\" However, this client seems to want to load the dll's from "C:\WINDOWS\.jagex_cache_32\". So copy your DL's from "C:\WINDOWS\.jagex_cache_32\runescape\" to "C:\WINDOWS\.jagex_cache_32\" See if that works for you.
[b]Credits[/b] - Javac Batch, dragonpkz for socket listener.
